{
  "stem": "20088.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my mother knew somebody who said she knew somebody as well, and it was a nurse who was going to provide a hiding place for my father.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father and brother had to escape from their hiding place because this woman wouldn't let them go, because it was a wonderful income for her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So she wanted more money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She still wanted them, really, to stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother dyed his hair blonde.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He bleached it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It became rather red.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was a bit embarrassed about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that he wouldn't, you know, look so-- and in the night-- so kind of the first train, 6 o'clock in the morning, they had to take the train to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the first time they had been going out for-- after two years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was, of course, terrible nerve-wracking and scary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would be met at the station by this nurse who would take them to their new hiding place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They would walk there, and they got there, and everything was all right.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They let-- but later, my father said he was suspicious because this nurse let herself in with her own key in this house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He thought that was odd.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know, never thinking about anything else besides this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first week, we went to visit there them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On a Saturday or Sunday, we went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't stay there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We just went to see them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We walked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And just to see how they were, and everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the evening, we walked home to this Mrs.-- to the Reitsma family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two days later we were sitting at breakfast.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
